metadata.title: Li'Shay Jewelry Armoire Cabinet Stand with 3 Drawers I Love Pretty Things
features: This is a beautiful chest to display on a shelf or dresser.
It measures 8.75 inches tall, 4.5 inches wide, and 3 inches deep.
Each of the 3 drawers has a gem-like handle and pulls out completely to find your valuables.
The front of the drawers have a cute message "I Love Pretty Things"!
Perfect Gift for any girl, teen or adult.
